research_municipality_step.notes: Information compiled from the TML City Officials Directory, Texas State Directory Online, and Whitewright City Council meeting minutes. There was a discrepancy regarding the Mayor Pro Tem, with one source listing Dustin Owens and others listing Traci Barr. Traci Barr was chosen as Mayor Pro Tem based on multiple sources, including recent meeting minutes. Additionally, Diana Scott was listed as present at a February 4, 2025 City Council meeting, but was not found in the provided directory listings for current officials.
